/**
# Download 

## Getting Basilisk 

Before downloading b-flood, basilisk must be installed on your
machine. To do this, you must go to [the web page dedicated to the
installation of Basilisk](/src/INSTALL) and follow the
instructions. Once done, go back to this page and continue the
installation.

## Getting b-flood 

To install the b-flood code, you have to download [this
tarball](b-flood.tgz) and decompress it in the basilisk/src/ directory
using

~~~bash
cd $BASILISK
tar xzvf b-flood.tgz
~~~

Please note that the code is exactly the same as on this website, so
you can walk around the site to discover the code.

## Link to the homepage

* [Homepage](Readme)
*/